<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <%= partial "head.html", assigns %>
  <body>
    <div class="homepage__content">
      <%= partial "login_top.html", assigns %>
      <div class="homepage__hero">
        
        <%= partial "header.html", assigns %>
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">NeverFap <span class="deluxe__font">Deluxe</span></h1>
        <h2 class="homepage__hero__title__secondary">The Comprehensive NoFap Companion.</h2>
      </div>
      
      <%= partial "links-patreon.html", assigns %>

      <div class="homepage__section">
      
        <p style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">My name is Julius and I'm a recovered porn addict. <i class="em em-blush"></i></p>
        <ul class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__list">
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item__lead">I no longer crave porn. <i class="em em-white_check_mark"></i></li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I no longer watch porn.</li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I don't even think about porn, at all.</li></span>
          <div class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__spacer"></div>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item__lead">I no longer obsess over women in public. <i class="em em-white_check_mark"></i></li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I no longer view women any differently to men.</li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I no longer judge women in any capacity.</li></span>
          
          <div class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__spacer"></div>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item__lead">I have control over my mind and my thoughts. <i class="em em-white_check_mark"></i></li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I'm conscious of my feelings and emotions.</li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I'm comfortable with my emotions, both positive and negative.</li></span>

          <div class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__spacer"></div>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item__lead">I accept myself for who I am. <i class="em em-white_check_mark"></i></li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I'm happy, motivated, confident and ambitious.</li></span>
          <span><li class="homepage__recovered__porn__addict__item">I'm unafraid of being vulnerable.</li></span>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--secondary">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">Here's what I do.</h1>
        <h2 class="homepage__hero__title__secondary">I explain step-by-step exactly how to give up porn.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>
          With the <b>NeverFap Deluxe Method</b>, I explain exactly how and why these steps work.
        </h3>
        <p>
          Because once you intuitively understand how something works, you will
          <u>commit to it forever.</u> <i class="em em-v"></i>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="account__info">
        <p class="account__info__title">Let's learn.</p>
      </div>      

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>The Method.</h1>

        <h2>It takes approximately 90 days to overcome porn addiction.</h2>
        <h3>It's called the <u>NeverFap Deluxe 90 Day Rule</u>, because those without healthy coping mechanisms rarely make it past 90 days.</h3>
        <p>In other words, if you can make it past 90 days without relapsing, it most likely means you've developed effective control over your mind.</p>
        <p>This control is what we aim to teach you.</p>
        <h2>In most cases, getting past the 90 day mark will usually signify the end of your porn addiction. Forever. <i class="em em-hushed"></i> </h2>
        <p>On the other hand, if you struggle to consistently get past 90 days, it most likely means you're approaching your recovery in a way that is ineffective.</p>
        <p>It's easy to get to 30 days or even 60 days using unhealthy coping mechanisms such as obsession, escapism, self-criticism or emotional dissociation.</p>
        <p>However, they almost always result in relapse. <i class="em em-ambulance"></i></p>
      </div>

      <div class="cyan__banner">
        <div class="cyan__banner__title__container">
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">Because a lot of</h2>
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title" style="color: rgba(255,46,182,1)">
            <div class="slidingVertical">
              <span>arguing with family members</span>
              <span>struggling with your career</span>
              <span>not caring about yourself</span>
              <span>dealing with toxic people</span>
              <span>feeling depressed and anxious</span>
              <span>pushing yourself way too hard</span>
              <span>life not going as planned</span>
            </div>.
          </h2>
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">can happen within 90 days.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>...and it's these situations where <span style="color: rgba(255,46,182,1);">unhealthy coping mechanisms</span> crumble.</h1>
        <h2>This is where 90% of relapse happens.</h2>
        <h3>Because unhealthy coping mechanisms don't help you deal with your emotions. They only help to supress them until they become unmanagable. Which is when you relapse.</h3>
        <h3>Relapse which could have been avoided, if only you had invested in healthy coping mechanisms which would have made dealing with those tough situations, trivial.</h3>
        <h3>Like, absurdly trivial.</h3>
        <p>I know in precise detail exactly what I need to do to keep my mind regulated and under control, and it's not even something I need to think about it anymore.</p>
        <p>Now imagine how awesome that would be.</p>
        <p>Because that's my life.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="magenta__banner">
        <div class="magenta__banner__title__container">
          <h2 class="magenta__banner__title">You see, overcoming porn addiction isn't really about <span class="text-flicker-out-glow">porn</span>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>Instead it's all about <span style="color: cyan;">developing control</span> over your mind.</h1>
        <h2>...and that's really all healthy coping mechanisms are.</h2>
        <h3>Skills and abilities which provide you with control over your mind, so that when your mind is under pressure, it doesn't collapse like a tower of cards.</h3>
        <p>For example, being able to remain calm and collected with a clear mind in difficult situations, rather than react in hesitation and give into our immediate desires.</p>

        <div class="five__principles__guide" >
          <h2 style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">Such as the ability to...</h2>
          <div class="five__principles__guide__item__cont"><div class="five__principles__guide__item">Value your mental health above all.</div></div>
          <div class="five__principles__guide__item__cont"><div class="five__principles__guide__item">Quiet and focus you mind.</div></div>
          <div class="five__principles__guide__item__cont"><div class="five__principles__guide__item">Love and accept youself unconditionally.</div></div>
          <div class="five__principles__guide__item__cont"><div class="five__principles__guide__item">Be confident about you recovery.</div></div>
          <div class="five__principles__guide__item__cont"><div class="five__principles__guide__item">Commit to long-term thinking.</div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="five__principles__guide--mobile">
          <h3>Value your mental health above all.</h3>
          <h3>Quiet and focus you mind.</h3>
          <h3>Love and accept youself unconditionally.</h3>
          <h3>Be confident about you recovery.</h3>
          <h3>Commit to long-term thinking.</h3>
        </div> 
        
        <h2>bleh.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="account__info">
        <p class="account__info__title">Making sense now?</p>
      </div>      

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>Skills which anyone can learn.</h1>
        <h3>(I'm looking at you, baby boy)</h3>
        <h3>Right now.</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="cyan__banner">
        <div class="cyan__banner__title__container">
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">So.</h2>
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">How.</h2>
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">Do you.</h2>
          <h2 class="cyan__banner__title">Develop these healthy coping mechanisms?</h2>   
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>By practicing those skills consistently.</h1>
        <h2>Don't even think about cheap work arounds. <span style="color: rgba(255,46,182,1);">I will hurt you.</span></h2>
        <h2>Practice and consistency are the only two things which matter to your recovery.</h2>
        <h3>Everything else is pure noise.</h3>
        <p>There are no cheap hacks, like putting a porn filter on your computer as if that's actually going to physically stop you from pursuing your addiction.</p>
        <p>It doesn't work.</p>
        <p>It never has. It never will.</p>
        <p>Although you're more than welcome to try ;)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="black__banner">
        <div class="black__banner__title__container">
          <h2 class="black__banner__title" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">Ultimately, there are three broad healthy coping mechanisms</br> <span class="black__banner__broad">NeverFap Deluxe</span> focuses on.</h2>
          <h1 class="black__banner__title black__banner__title--cat">Awareness</h1>
          <h1 class="black__banner__title black__banner__title--cat">Calmness</h1>
          <h1 class="black__banner__title black__banner__title--cat">Ambition</h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h1>Most people are severely deficient in one or two of these areas.</h1>
        
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">

          7 day kickstarter plan. 

        <h1>You want to stop being a porn addict?</h1>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">It's really not that hard.</h2>

        <div class="homepage__process">
          <span><h3 class="homepage__process__title">
            Read the articles.
          </h3></span>
          <!-- <p class="homepage__process__text">Find out exactly which skills you will need to learn.</p>  -->
          <p class="homepage__process__text">Understand exactly why NeverFap works.</p> <!-- Understand the skills required to help you overcome porn addiction, and understand exactly how and why they work in precise detail. -->
        </div>
        <span><a class="homepage__process__link" href="/articles">Link to articles.</a></span>

        <div class="homepage__process">
          <span><h3 class="homepage__process__title">
            Practice the exercises.
          </h3></span>
          <!-- <p class="homepage__process__text">Practice these skills on a daily basis.</p> -->
          <p class="homepage__process__text">Develop healthy coping mechanisms with daily practice.</p>
        </div>
        <span><a class="homepage__process__link" href="/articles">Link to exercises.</a></span>

        <div class="homepage__process">
          <span><h3 class="homepage__process__title">
            Complete the courses.
          </h3></span>
          <%#  <p class="homepage__process__text">Practice these skills on a daily basis.</p>  %>
          <p class="homepage__process__text">Learn new skills based on proven pathways.</p>
        </div>
        <span><a class="homepage__process__link" href="/articles">Link to courses.</a></span>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">It's really not that hard. <i class="em em-cake"></i></h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Check out the NeverFap Deluxe Guide for <u>further instruction</u>!</p>
      </div>

      <%= partial "links-boxLink.html", %{ title: "Guide", text: "You should definitely click on me. Pleeeease.", link: "/guide" } %>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">Furthermore, all of these articles and practices have been organised into...</h3>
        <h2>The Five Fundmental Principles of NeverFap!</h2>
        <ul class="five__principles__list__main">
          <span><li class="five__principles__item__main">Choice over mind</li></span>
          <span><li class="five__principles__item__main">Balance over reward</li></span>
          <span><li class="five__principles__item__main">Struggle over none</li></span>
          <span><li class="five__principles__item__main">Awareness over all</li></span>
          <span><li class="five__principles__item__main__judgement">Uncondition over judgement</li></span>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <%= partial "links-boxLink.html", %{ title: "Principles", text: "Learn more about The Five Fundamental Principles of NeverFap.", link:  "/articles/the-five-fundamental-principles-of-neverfap" } %>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>Hooray!</h3>
        <h2>
          The Five Fundamental Principles of NeverFap make
          addressing your porn addiction a breeze.
        </h2>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">It's what this entire website has been built upon. <i class="em em-bank"></i></h3>
        <div class="button__wrapper">
          <a
            class="button"
            href="/articles/the-five-fundamental-principles-of-neverfap"
            >Learn More About The Five Principles.</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--secondary">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">The NeverFap Deluxe Guide.</h1>
        <h2 class="homepage__hero__title__secondary">A series of articles to help explain the NeverFap method.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h2>Here are a selection of our top articles to help get you started:</h2>
        <hr style="margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;"/>

