      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section"  style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <h2>Warning! <i class="em em-warning"></i></h2>
        <h3>
          Chances are that you may have been going about porn recovery the wrong
          way.
        </h3>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--third">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">If you believe you have limited control over your mind.</h1>
        <ul class="homepage__hero__principle__wrapper">
          <li class="homepage__hero__principle__item">Choice over mind</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>You're doing it wrong. <i class="em em-x"></i></h3>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--third">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">If you struggle to get further than two months.</h1>
        <ul class="homepage__hero__principle__wrapper">
          <li class="homepage__hero__principle__item">Balance over reward</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>You're doing it wrong. <i class="em em-x"></i></h3>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--third">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">If you consistently fight your emotions.</h1>
        <ul class="homepage__hero__principle__wrapper">
          <li class="homepage__hero__principle__item">Struggle over none</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>You're doing it wrong. <i class="em em-x"></i></h3>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--third">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">If you don't practice meditation.</h1>
        <ul class="homepage__hero__principle__wrapper">
          <li class="homepage__hero__principle__item">Awareness over all</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>You're doing it wrong. <i class="em em-x"></i></h3>
        <hr />
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__hero homepage__hero--third">
        <h1 class="homepage__hero__title">If you are critical of yourself and others.</h1>
        <ul class="homepage__hero__principle__wrapper">
          <li class="homepage__hero__principle__item">Uncondition over judgement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>You get the drift. <i class="em em-anguished"></i></h3>
        <hr />
