      <div class="homepage__section">
        <h3>Listen...</h3>
        <h1>I've spent most my life doing it wrong.</h1>
        <h2>So you don't have to waste your time like I did. <i class="em em-innocent"></i></h2>
        <hr />
        <p>Click on the link below to get started with your NeverFap journey:</p>

